\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ksm1665702577277.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ksm1665702577277.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ksm1665702577277.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ksm1665702577277\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n $instancename\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ksm1665702577277___instancename_269904\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the current component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__topic_d84686e1_d84687e1_d84688e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__p_d84689e1_d84690e1_d84691e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__topic_d56117e1_d56118e1_d56119e1_d56120e1_d56121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d530044e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__li_d34544e1_d34545e1_d34546e1\">Name of current component instance in uppercase.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__li_d34547e1_d34548e1_d34549e1\">Name of the current form in uppercase, if the form was started with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">run</span>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__li_d34550e1_d34551e1_d34552e1\">Name of the application shell, if no form is current (for example, in the apStart trigger).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__li_d34553e1_d34554e1_d34555e1\">Empty string (\"\"), if an error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1304</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ksm1665702577277__table_d8831e1_d8832e1_d8833e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Function not allowed, unknown context.\n <p class=\"p\">For example, there is no current instance in the apStart trigger, or the current instance is a form started with <code class=\"ph codeph\">run</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__topic_d56122e1_d56123e1_d56124e1_d56125e1_d56126e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d530044e162\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__p_d84698e1_d84699e1_d84700e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__section_g2y_f41_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d530044e171\">Example: Tracing Application Execution</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">You can use the value in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancename</span> to help\n               trace an application's execution. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ksm1665702577277__pre_syv_g41_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\nputmess \"Started instance %%$instancename at %%$clock\"\nedit\nputmess \"Terminated instance %%$instancename at %%$clock\"\nend ; end exec\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pvq1719930730570.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancepath</a><p>Return the path with which the current component instance is registered.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ndl1665702597453.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$componentname</a><p>Return the name of the component from which the specified instance was created.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jti1665702695275.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$formname (deprecated)</a><p>Return the name of the current Form component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529354\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529354\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$instancename Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. $instancename Return Values Name of current component instance in uppercase. Name of the current form in uppercase, if the form was started with run . Name of the application shell, if no form is current (for example, in the apStart trigger). Empty string (\"\"), if an error occurred. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $instancename Value Error constant Meaning -1304 <UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT> Function not allowed, unknown context. For example, there is no current instance in the apStart trigger, or the current instance is a form started with run . Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Tracing Application Execution You can use the value in $instancename to help trace an application's execution. For example: operation exec putmess \"Started instance %%$instancename at %%$clock\" edit putmess \"Terminated instance %%$instancename at %%$clock\" end ; end exec Copy Related Links $instancepath Return the path with which the current component instance is registered. $componentname Return the name of the component from which the specified instance was created. $formname (deprecated) Return the name of the current Form component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}